      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense but it still feels like the interest is just eating up my money. specifically when i look at the math for the first year, it feels like there are these extra costs or things that just keep adding up in the background making it harder to pay it off. why does it feel like the interest is working against me so much more at the start?",
